ons of the\nextended Q-system. We conjecture that the extended Q-system constrained in such\na way is always in bijection with the Bethe algebra of commuting transfer\nmatrices of these models and moreover can be used to show that the Bethe\nalgebra has a simple joint spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Aug 2020 17:59:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Jan 2021 19:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-11"}
